Usage: mwdev [<stuff>]

--config                              Configure stuff!
--clone --<type> <name>               Clones the extension or skin into the correct directory
--code-review params...               Interacts with Gerrit
--report                              Stuff to help you manage extensions
--missing                             Lists missing annexes and optionally clones them with --get
--msg-hook                            Adds the Gerrit commit-msg hook to the git repo you are in
--pull-all                            Pulls all of something
--composer                            Updates a requirement in a composer.json file for a given skin or extension
--help                                Provides help. (Can be used with commands listed above)
